{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/Grinch_SteamBanner_Eng_1.png?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>Sneak and steal presents as the Grinch and his dog Max.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/HAVE_AWFULLY_GOOD_FUN_Frame.gif?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>Have a great Grinchy time trying to steal Christmas in this festive platformer \u2013 and help the Grinch\u2019s small heart grow a few sizes bigger along the way!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/Grinch_SteamBanner_Eng_3.png?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>Solve puzzles to gain abilities! Throw snowballs, disguise as Santa, use a Candy Cane Lasso or a Jumping Jetpack, and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/UNLOCK_GRINCHY_GADGETS_Frame.gif?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>Every Who down in Who-ville loves to sing, gift and feast, which are all of the things Grinch can\u2019t stand in the least. So, help the Grinch and his dog Max set out to steal all the presents in Who-ville. You\u2019ll have to be sneaky to avoid the bothersome babble of carol singers, the ever-eager Whos, and all of the tinsel, trimmings and trappings of the Christmas season.  <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/Grinch_SteamBanner_Eng_2.png?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>The Grinch wants to stop Christmas, but you can help his heart grow three sizes! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/GET_IN_THE_SPIRIT_Frame.gif?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>Thankfully, the Grinch has some wonderful, awful ideas \u2013 like a Santa costume for stealthy sneaking, a Candy Cane Lasso to swing around, a speedy snowboard that can reach special race areas, and more. And Grinch can throw snowballs to freeze any pesky creatures that get in his way.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/Grinch_SteamBanner_Eng_4.png?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>With visuals inspired by Dr. Seuss\u2019s book and controls for young players.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978210/extras/EXPERIENCE_A_CLASSIC_Frame.gif?t=1701706239\" /><br><br>With colorful visuals inspired by Dr. Seuss\u2019s original illustrations, local multiplayer fun with up to two players controlling the Grinch and Max, and controls and puzzles designed for younger players, The Grinch: Christmas Adventures is a fun new way to enjoy the classic Christmas tale.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Use Max","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/1f66fa338e2f99d894a6be81cfc14e8c1f52c9f3.jpg"},{"name":"Jump over","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/ba27df1a31309db86e06ed1c0f0666288d117017.jpg"},{"name":"First Puzzle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/7ada479bcd06651920856b8f859ed7ec8e54428c.jpg"},{"name":"Double Jump","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/278ecd284c8e72987084a34f38064f72bb386c1b.jpg"},{"name":"Candy Cane Lasso","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/cebd3ff2a3cb3e339d51b6a8d66146b876bd5ee0.jpg"},{"name":"The Grinch's Cave","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/059deaaed0bc19aeeda65a0224e5ae522abf7524.jpg"},{"name":"Presents","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1978210/9d86a39089b011d6237a1a40b8a8fc6ddf1472c1.jpg"},{"name":"Santa","